[section#conv.array
    [:en] Array-to-pointer conversion
    [:zh_CN] 数组向指针转换
]

[para]
[:en] [%conversion[!array-to-pointer]]
[%decay[!array] [%conversion[!array-to-pointer]]]
[%decay[!function] [%conversion[!function-to-pointer]]]
An expression [$E] of type [=lq]array of [`N] [`T][=rq] or [=lq]array of unknown
bound of [`T][=rq] can be converted to a prvalue of type [=lq]pointer to [`T][=rq].
[:zh_CN] [%转换[!数组向指针～]]
[%退化[!数组] [%转换[!数组向指针～]]]
[%退化[!函数] [%转换[!函数向指针～]]]
类型“[`T] 的 [`N] 元数组”或“[`T] 的边界未知数组”的表达式 [$E]，可被转换为类型“[`T] 的指针”的纯右值。

[:en] If [$E] is a prvalue, the temporary materialization conversion ([#conv.rval]) is applied.
[:zh_CN] 如果 [$E] 是纯右值，则实施临时对象实质化转换（[#conv.rval]）。

[:en] If the result of [$E] (possibly converted) is an object whose type is similar
to the type of [$E], the result is a pointer to the first element of the array;
otherwise, the behavior is undefined.
[:zh_CN] 如果 [$E]（可能已转换）的结果是类型与 [$E] 的类型相似的对象，
其结果是指向该数组第一个元素的指针；否则，其行为未定义。
